00:32:33,588 --> 00:32:34,589
Ayah memanggilku?

424
00:32:39,594 --> 00:32:40,762
<i>Kedai Terhebat.</i>

425
00:32:42,555 --> 00:32:43,765
Biaya apa ini?

426
00:32:46,309 --> 00:32:47,685
Harusnya mereka membayar kita.

427
00:32:51,105 --> 00:32:52,273
Ini?

428
00:32:53,942 --> 00:32:55,985
Saeroyi ingin tampil di sini.

429
00:32:56,444 --> 00:32:58,112
Jadi, aku bayar mereka
