447
00:34:15,648 --> 00:34:17,150
Aku datang karena dipanggil Ayah.

448
00:34:21,446 --> 00:34:22,530
Kenapa kau dipanggil?

449
00:34:28,036 --> 00:34:29,746
Aku tanya, kenapa Ayah memanggilmu.

450
00:34:34,292 --> 00:34:35,460
Kau khawatir?

